<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CE2DD103FF93AA35755C0A9669C8B63&amp;pagewanted=print" class="external text" title="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CE2DD103FF93AA35755C0A9669C8B63&amp;pagewanted=print" rel="nofollow">FILM REVIEW; From Blaxploitation Stereotype to Man on the Street - New York Times</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;token=ADFEAEE47C17D24EAA7520F7A61A74E1915DDA2AFF71D6BD310E6A6CFD9D1E67C32E59CC40F0ABAEC5FC3FCF7BE3F931A65B10D1CAEE51B0DB6C3E3E87EAAE705843&amp;sql=77:11040" class="external text" title="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;token=ADFEAEE47C17D24EAA7520F7A61A74E1915DDA2AFF71D6BD310E6A6CFD9D1E67C32E59CC40F0ABAEC5FC3FCF7BE3F931A65B10D1CAEE51B0DB6C3E3E87EAAE705843&amp;sql=77:11040" rel="nofollow">"Music Genre: Blaxploitation"</a>. Allmusic<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;token=ADFEAEE47C17D24EAA7520F7A61A74E1915DDA2AFF71D6BD310E6A6CFD9D1E67C32E59CC40F0ABAEC5FC3FCF7BE3F931A65B10D1CAEE51B0DB6C3E3E87EAAE705843&amp;sql=77:11040" class="external free" title="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;token=ADFEAEE47C17D24EAA7520F7A61A74E1915DDA2AFF71D6BD310E6A6CFD9D1E67C32E59CC40F0ABAEC5FC3FCF7BE3F931A65B10D1CAEE51B0DB6C3E3E87EAAE705843&amp;sql=77:11040" rel="nofollow">http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;token=ADFEAEE47C17D24EAA7520F7A61A74E1915DDA2AFF71D6BD310E6A6CFD9D1E67C32E59CC40F0ABAEC5FC3FCF7BE3F931A65B10D1CAEE51B0DB6C3E3E87EAAE705843&amp;sql=77:11040</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-06-21</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Music+Genre%3A+Blaxploitation&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Allmusic&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.allmusic.com%2Fcg%2Famg.dll%3Fp%3Damg%26token%3DADFEAEE47C17D24EAA7520F7A61A74E1915DDA2AFF71D6BD310E6A6CFD9D1E67C32E59CC40F0ABAEC5FC3FCF7BE3F931A65B10D1CAEE51B0DB6C3E3E87EAAE705843%26sql%3D77%3A11040&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Blaxploitation"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
