<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Blaxploitation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.blaxploitation.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.blaxploitation.com/" rel="nofollow">Blaxploitation.com</a> — A comprehensive database on blaxploitation films, soundtracks and artwork.</li>
<li><a href="http://194.78.207.186/BB/admin/ReelNewsDetail.asp?ID=2734" class="external text" title="http://194.78.207.186/BB/admin/ReelNewsDetail.asp?ID=2734" rel="nofollow">An overview of the history of Blaxploitation</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.grindhousedatabase.com/index.php/Category:Blaxploitation" class="external text" title="http://www.grindhousedatabase.com/index.php/Category:Blaxploitation" rel="nofollow">Listing of Blaxploitation films</a> at THE DEUCE: Grindhouse Cinema Database</li>
<li><a href="http://funkmasterj.tripod.com/blax.html" class="external text" title="http://funkmasterj.tripod.com/blax.html" rel="nofollow">Comprehensive listing of blaxploitation links</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.formatmag.com/reviews/blaxploitation-films/" class="external text" title="http://www.formatmag.com/reviews/blaxploitation-films/" rel="nofollow">An introduction to Blaxploitation Films</a></li>
<li><a href="http://foxybronx.free.fr/" class="external text" title="http://foxybronx.free.fr/" rel="nofollow">FoxyBronx.fr</a> <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(French)</span></li>
<li><a href="http://www.science-digtion.de/" class="external text" title="http://www.science-digtion.de/" rel="nofollow">The science of Rare Groove Diggin, including Blaxploitation, of course</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.maderfaker.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.maderfaker.com/" rel="nofollow">Maderfaker Industry</a> — a space devoted to Blaxploitation films</li>
<li><a href="http://www.separatecinema.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.separatecinema.com/" rel="nofollow">Separate Cinema Archive</a> — reflects the history and legacy of the African American cultural contribution to cinema.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.blackhorrormovies.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.blackhorrormovies.com/" rel="nofollow">Black Horror Movies</a></li>
</ul>


